</p>
<p>exchange and financial crises, devaluation and default, see Damill, Frenkel and Rapetti, &#8220;The 
Argentinean debt&#8221;, p. 38. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>4
 The convertibility plan in effect prohibited the devaluation of the peso to increase exports. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>5
